@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ckxftr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v1 = wp.cos(0.29)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.cos(tmp + 0.40) + (v0 + 0.37 / tmp + 0.96)))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.sin(tmp + 0.80) - wp.exp(v1 + 0.87)))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.78)))
    data[tid] = v0
